":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom","pa_condition_repeater":[]},"elements":[{"id":"19a8a255","settings":{"_column_size":100,"_inline_size":null,"space_between_widgets":0,"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[{"id":"37bf2e57","settings":{"editor":"<p class=\"fl-heading\"><span class=\"fl-heading-text\">Summary<\/span><\/p>","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":30,"sizes":[]},"typography_font_weight":"700","_margin":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom","__globals__":{"text_color":"globals\/colors?id=primary"}},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"1f990989","settings":{"editor":"<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">Join us for an insightful webinar with <strong>Adam Loewentheil<\/strong>, an expert in engineering and consulting workflows, as he shares key strategies to streamline operations, reduce administrative burdens, and leverage modern technology to improve efficiency and profitability.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Why Attend?<\/strong><\/p>\n<ol class=\"ProsemirrorEditor-list\">\n<li class=\"ProsemirrorEditor-listItem\" data-list-indent=\"1\" data-list-type=\"bulleted\">\n<p>Gain practical, actionable tips to improve efficiency and profitability.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"ProsemirrorEditor-listItem\" data-list-indent=\"1\" data-list-type=\"bulleted\">\n<p>Learn about emerging technology trends that will shape engineering firms in the next five years.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"ProsemirrorEditor-listItem\" data-list-indent=\"1\" data-list-type=\"bulleted\">\n<p>Understand how to leverage AI and automation without compromising quality.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><strong>Who Should Attend?<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Engineers, consultants, project managers, and firm leaders looking to optimize operations, maximize productivity, and stay ahead in an evolving industry.<\/p>\n<p>Don\u2019t miss this opportunity to gain <strong>practical, actionable insights<\/strong> that will help your firm work smarter and grow faster.<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:fl-builder\/layout --><\/p>","pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"56830ffe","settings":{"editor":"<p class=\"fl-heading\"><b>Your Speaker<\/b><\/p>","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":30,"sizes":[]},"typography_font_weight":"700","_margin":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"30","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom","__globals__":{"text_color":"globals\/colors?id=primary"}},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"3bdcad1a","settings":{"editor":"<h2 data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">Adam Loewentheil, Co-Founder &amp; CEO, Aldoa<\/h2>","_margin":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"5c16b1b3","settings":{"editor":"<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"><a href=\"https:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Adam-Lowentheil.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-73400\" title=\"Adam Loewentheil, Co-Founder &amp; CEO, Aldoa\" src=\"https:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Adam-Lowentheil.jpg\" alt=\"Aldoa\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" \/><\/a>Following in the footsteps of three generations of builders, Adam witnessed firsthand the inefficiencies afflicting the environmental consulting &amp; engineering industry. He\u2019s passionate about building software solutions to empower consultants and engineers to focus more on what they do best: delivering quality work to their clients. Prior to founding Aldoa, Adam was a financial analyst at a leading hedge fund in NYC.<\/p>","_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"31e72a6c","settings":{"editor":"<p class=\"fl-heading\"><b>Your Host<\/b><\/p>","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":30,"sizes":[]},"typography_font_weight":"700","_margin":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"30","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom","__globals__":{"text_color":"globals\/colors?id=primary"}},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"4adb6f63","settings":{"editor":"<h2 class=\"fl-heading\"><b>Anthony Fasano, P.E., AEC PM | Engineering Management Institute<\/b><\/h2>","_margin":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"},{"id":"745eb11d","settings":{"editor":"<p><a href=\"https:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/Anthony-Fasano.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-55130 size-medium\" title=\"Anthony Fasano, P.E., AEC PM\" src=\"https:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/Anthony-Fasano-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"EMI- Your Engineering Career\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Most AEC organizations are too busy to focus on attracting, developing, and retaining talented professionals, making it hard to grow. Through his work a tEMI, Fasano utilizes a proven framework to help organizations, both public and private, build professional development plans, programs, and tools that help them attract, build, AND maintain strong teams and grow sustainably.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fasano has written a bestselling book entitled <\/span><b><i>Engineer Your Own Success <\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">(by IEEE-Wiley Press)<\/span><\/i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, and under his stewardship, EMI has built a massive content platform including 10 active podcasts, 3 YouTube channels, and a popular blog dedicated to helping AEC professionals become better managers and leaders.<\/span><\/p>","_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"50","left":"0","isLinked":false},"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":true,"elType":"column"}],"isInner":true,"elType":"section"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"column"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"section"}],"settings":{"template":"elementor_canvas"},"metadata":{"_yoast_wpseo_estimated-reading-time-minutes":"3","_yoast_wpseo_content_score":"90","be_title_toggle_hide":"1","disable_sitewide_pop